        "timestamp": "2018-10-23 22:42:28.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI feel like we should be cherry picking from casablanca back to master and merging individually.\n\nFYI in a couple weeks the jenkins job will be gone. We will have no record of what was added to master from casablanca branch.",
