        "timestamp": "2018-10-24 12:49:44.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nCherry Picking individually will leave missed commits, I am not sure your hesitation with pulling all commits periodically between branches.  This is fairly normal gerrit/git semantics",
